{"tid":2284249,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"刁你老味吖，即係你講撚曬","createTime":"2020-11-13T06:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T07:09:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eab231bacee39bb3462591201aca36bb1f3e369e","tid":2284249,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"刁你老味吖，即係你講撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/HISVBHSKBBAAVMD7GWWWBSXKI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FHISVBHSKBBAAVMD7GWWWBSXKI4%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIkHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=73d7d003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FHISVBHSKBBAAVMD7GWWWBSXKI4%2F&h=16acc5b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/HISVBHSKBBAAVMD7GWWWBSXKI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠降溫：人大非針對拉布<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/539OcLq8v9VAJfdyHpK-I5nbVGg=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ULJGM7G5NJFKHF7GPNRJCBRVVE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F539OcLq8v9VAJfdyHpK-I5nbVGg%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FULJGM7G5NJFKHF7GPNRJCBRVVE.JPG&h=d1685ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚惠珠<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人大常委會泰山壓頂強劃紅線，頒佈DQ民主派議員「決定」，同時訂出的愛國者標準，如同令立法會武功盡廢。有建制派連日來一直放風，指拉布應被DQ，甚至「擺領導人上枱」，指全因有領導人觀看立法會直播，覺得拉布情況過份，忍無可忍於是出手「處決」民主派。不過，基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠昨又突把人大常委會的「決定」跟拉布劃清界線，指「決定」並非針對議員拉布，更指人大的文件並無說到拉布問題。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美加德澳歐盟痛斥中共DQ議員  英將制裁林鄭政府<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠昨早出席電台節目時，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱議員可上訴<br />\n<br />\n至於法律界批評，「決定」繞過法院DQ議員，譚辯稱人大「決定」沒有「掃走」任何司法程序，亦不剝奪「司法補救」，有關議員仍可在法律上作選舉呈請或司法覆核，甚至指最終說不定會勝訴，又或因違反港版國安法被法庭裁定有罪也可提出上訴，但在「決定」下要先離開議會，得直後重回議會「是另一回事」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如選舉主任DQ參選資格決定被法院推翻，四名被取消資格議員是否能重回議會，譚指人大常委會已特別就四人資格作決定，相信將不能重返議會。至於是否終身剝奪參選資格，她指按其理解，違反國安法而喪失資格會被終身剝奪參選權，但今次四名議員只是損害香港利益，未至於危害國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n不睇由自可 一睇把鬼火<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc02e4e7ad6d84816b828e248e8491628731e424","tid":2284249,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"唔好post樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到佢個樣就憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}